# Documentation of all links I used to get my SVGs
I created this in order to avoid searching things twice whenever I may need to edit the background color of a single SVG  
If you need to change the background color, just change the HEX color in either one of the following links you need and you're good to go... At least, I hope you won't need to change the SVG, too!
